[For those who are confused, as of 1 Nov 2005 the cumulative number
of WHO-authenticated laboratory-confirmed cases since 2003 stands at:
Cambodia, 4 cases including 4 deaths; Indonesia, 7 cases including 4
deaths; Thailand, 20 cases including 13 deaths; Viet Nam, 91 cases
including 41 deaths; and the total for East Asia, 122 cases including
62 deaths. - Mod.CP]
